Unused assets of War Thunder

As of version 2.53.0.56.

My focus is on user assets, so map assets are excluded.

Credit to Michal9787 for the better looking model and skin images.

Disclaimer: This is not a definite list of upcoming additions! The older items will probably never see the light of day.

Ground vehicle belts, shells, and missiles
  • Most of these are due to more than one tank using the same cannon file, but with restricted shells.
  • The lack of low-tier HE was an intentional change by Gaijin to prevent newbies running around with HE, achieving absolutely nothing, and leaving the game.
